page.title: 03A Day in my Life (cont)
page.content: TAKE OFF MY COAT AND SHOES AND PUT MY BAG DOWN.I GO UP INTO MY BEDROOM AND GET CHANGED.I PUT ON MY JEANS AND JUMPER ON THEN I GO DOWNSTAIRS. I HAVE A DRINK AND SOME BISCUITS.I WATCH SOME TELEVISION.AT ABOUT 6:00 WE HAVE OUR DINNER.MY FAVOURITE TELEVISION PROGRAMME IS GRANGE HILL AND MY FAVOURITE DINNER IS SPEGETTI BOLANAISE I GO SWIMMING AT 8:05 AT BISHOP STORTFORD.WE GET HOME FROM SWIMMING CLUB AT 9:45.I PUT MY PYJAMAS ON THEY ARE YELLOW.I GO AND CLEAN MY TEETH. I GET INTO BED AND GO TO SLEEP.
